
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>.NET Full Stack Course</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2027, #203a43, #2c5364);
            color: #fff;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

            header h1 {
                font-size: 3rem;
                color: #00d4ff;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            header p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                max-width: 600px;
                margin: auto;
            }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background: #00d4ff;
            color: #000;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

            .btn:hover {
                background: #fff;
                color: #203a43;
            }

        section {
            padding: 60px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .features {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            width: 280px;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

            .card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }

            .card h3 {
                color: #00d4ff;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }

        footer {
            background: #111;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #aaa;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Become a .NET Full Stack Developer</h1>
        <p>Master ASP.NET Core, Angular, Web API, and modern deployment practices with our hands-on course designed for real-world projects.</p>
        <a href="#enroll" class="btn">Enroll Now</a>
    </header>

    <section>
        <h2>Why Choose This Course?</h2>
        <div class="features">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>🔥 Real Projects</h3>
                <p>Work on enterprise-level applications to build confidence and experience.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>⚡ Full Stack Skills</h3>
                <p>Learn both front-end (Angular) and back-end (.NET Core) development.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>🌐 Deployment Ready</h3>
                <p>Understand Azure cloud deployment and API versioning for production apps.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="enroll">
        <h2>Limited Seats Available!</h2>
        <p>Don’t miss your chance to become a certified .NET Full Stack Developer.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn">Register Today</a>
    </section>

    <footer>
        © 2026 .NET Full Stack Academy | Designed with ❤️
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Simple animation for header text
        const header = document.querySelector("header h1");
        let colors = ["#00d4ff", "#ff4081", "#ffd740"];
        let i = 0;
        setInterval(() => {
          header.style.color = colors[i % colors.length];
          i++;
        }, 2000);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
